\/2021\/07\/26\/muhammad-dua-salat-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: The Prophet shown supplications for him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud al-Ansari reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your blessings upon me on Friday, for no one blesses me on Friday but that his prayer is presented to me.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 2769 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/expiate-sins-increase-rewards\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Deeds to expiate sins, increase rewards","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of that by which Allah expiates your sins and increases your good deeds?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThorough ablution despite difficulty, taking many steps to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/salah-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet stresses the greatness of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he asked him about the best of deeds. The Prophet said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen prayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/06\/prayer-reconciliation-good-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Prayer, reconciliation, good character best deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 6, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam does not act with anything better than prayer, reconciliation between people, and good character.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 10579 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/increase-dua-prophet-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Supplications for the Prophet on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your supplications for me on the day and night of Friday. Whoever blesses me once, Allah will bless him ten times.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5994 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32033,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/salat-on-time-safe-lisan\/","url_meta":{"origin":42443,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Best deed to pray on time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deeds are best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer on time.\u201d I said, \u201cThen what, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood treatment of your parents.\u201d I said, \u201cThen what, O Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u064